# Gold Ticker Live — Cursor Agent Rules

## Project
- Static site: Vanilla ES6, Vite, GitHub Pages
- Backend: Supabase (shop data, RLS policies active)
- Automation: GitHub Actions (8+ workflows, do not break them)
- API: goldpricez.com (replaces gold-api.com — do not revert)
- Hosting: goldtickerlive.com via Cloudflare DNS

## Non-negotiables
- Never mix spot price with retail/jewelry shop prices
- Always label cached, estimated, or fallback values clearly
- AED peg = 3.6725 (fixed, do not derive dynamically)
- Troy ounce = 31.1035g (constant)
- RTL support must be preserved on every change (Arabic = /ar)
- Never remove freshness labels or price disclaimers

## Code rules
- Smallest correct change only — no refactors unless asked
- Preserve all existing tests (205 tests) — run tests before marking done
- Do not add new dependencies without asking
- Output: working code only, no placeholder TODOs

## Before any PR
- Run: npm test
- Check: RTL layout not broken
- Check: price labels are accurate
- Check: no console errors on goldtickerlive.com equivalent build
